  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The pulmonary veins are the predominant sources of AF induction and maintenance. This study
      aims to assess the electrophysiological properties of the pulmonary veins and their relation
      to AF in humans.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
